data.name: lblInstructions.Text
data.value: - For Medium-type tanks you should not stand with them - Always be on the lookout for enemy tanks near your base. Remember it's game over if the base is destroyed - A risky way to play is to stay in the position where the enemy tanks appear and shoot as soon as the enemy tanks appear, this is dangerous if 3 enemy tanks appear at the same time - If an item appears but you face dangerous enemies. Who knows what might happen while you eat that item - Don't let yourself be surrounded by enemy tanks - Finally, don't let the first stages of the game fool you. You will soon find out that enemy tanks have good AI
